[center][i][u][b]DESCRIPTION:[/b][/u]

New World is a new country, which is now waiting to be brought to life.

Added 421 new objects... houses, castle, and more...

with weather, original skyrim music...

a fantastic world of animals and great scenery

Each modder can create his own yard, or use my building with the CreationsKit.

go very well for hunting or Modder Resorce

in the coastal area is my new Japan House(see the MapMarker in New World)

can be reached Rochester with Teleport spell. The Spell Book finds in Whiterun, see Images.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

[u][b]Delete the Rochester File from Skyrim and copy New World (Masterfile).esm and bsa to Skyrim Datafolder.[/b][/u]


... Try and Enjoy it ...

breti
